---
title: Easy Chorizo, Potato & Almond Tray Bake with Greek Salad Cheese & Balsamic Glaze
description: Leave it up to chorizo to do the heavy lifting in this dish that’s big on flavour and scant on effort. Tray baking veg with this feisty Spanish sausage ensures none of the amazing flavour is lost to your pan – it all ends up in your mouth!
